REM Friendly starter payload. Opens the OS launcher, types "notepad"
REM and writes two lines. Works on Windows (Win+R), macOS (Cmd+Space)
REM and most Linux desktops (Super opens the activity overview).

DEFAULTDELAY 50

GUI SPACE
DELAY 600
STRING notepad
DELAY 200
ENTER
DELAY 1500
STRINGLN Hello, world!
STRINGLN Typed by StrykerOSS over USB HID.
